Author: hammerprice
Text: I have to be either empty and feeling hungry and productive (why are those two things linked in my brain??) OR full to the point where I don't think I could eat any more. If I am anywhere in between then it's like I click over into binge mode.  Also you're allowed to say this here, this is totally understandable venting and you're not alone. I hope you can find it not to punish yourself tomorrow for eating a dinner you need but we are here for you. xo
